{"tid":1242833,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年 超實用BBQ安全注意事項","createTime":"2019-06-19T08:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:54:42.000Z","uid":198309,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b2175fc0046dec99567f216b4d6c14b1715c65c","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9go3po.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9go3po.jpg&h=3e993083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家都想快啲到秋天 快啲燒烤 係唔係?<br />\n但大家都唔係成日燒烤 所以細佬今日教大家燒烤嘅事前同事後處理<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>事前準備</ins></span><br />\n正所謂打邊爐最緊要係個爐 點解?<br />\n因為個爐有火 而火釋出<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱能</span></span>(例如炭) 就可以整熟啲野<br />\n換而之燒烤都係咁 有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱能</span></span>(例如炭)就可以開始bbq<br />\n另外一樣就係個網 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eNn7LOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeNn7LOt.jpg&h=772e9d9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲網最緊要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越密越好</span></span> 費事啲野食跌落去就唔好啦係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>事後處理</ins></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">bbq完之後最緊要係熄火！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">bbq完之後最緊要係熄火！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">bbq完之後最緊要係熄火！！！</span><br />\n好重要所以講三次<br />\n相信大家用開炭黎生火 而啲炭燒完野食之後咁熱 點拎得起啊?<br />\n唔洗驚 有以下呢樣野就冇有怕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05xWD2w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05xWD2w.jpg&h=a6fe46fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇錯就係啱先夾野食燒嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鉗</span></span>喇！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">除此之外</span></span>你仲要一兜水去擺啲炭入去 有位巴打之前整左 係拎個plastic bottle剪開佢在裝啲水入去 就咁拎個鉗夾啲炭落去就得喇！<br />\n記住擺啲炭入去會有好多煙 記得用個蓋com翻好佢<br />\n如果驚辣親手嘅可以試下帶<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防熱手套</span></span> 記得連埋鉗一齊用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n唔該大家share開去 等更多人知道燒烤嘅準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望呢篇文可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e970fd1032d8207b183c7773458762cdd4fb61c4","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228eaa3133f4289065bff6e9e3adec42b9a79abf","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3410c7b14382e0aba95d325f5a7d332487edfbb4","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63fe636036b0e50706952b4bc34505155cd90edd","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5425eb87ae9d6693e1ab200dbdb6350b1ffa7ab7","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424692ccb1b123bda2430469c35099a09765f421","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22de4200d010be420d5bd0110dd4a99e6e4ac49","tid":1242833,"uid":198309,"like":0,"d